\id ROM - initial draft done by Francis Dagonov, Irwin Kuabe, Steven Marguma, and David Berama, Nov 98-done in Epistle Workshop at Ukarumpa, lead by Ed Condra; Some revisions done by Steven Feb 99; prep for exeg ck by Marsha Sept 2000; exeg ck by Francis and Marsha Aug 03; comp ck by Siria and Pais Asuari and John R and Marsha Sept 03; consultant ck Nov 03 by Mike Sweeney with Steven, John O, John Stanley, Asefi, Martin, John R, and Marsha; ready for publication. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus.
\h Rom
\toc3 RO
\toc2 Rom
\toc1 Ak…®nafarir Pol Rom…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n Itir Sios Bagha Osirizim
\mt1 Ak…®nafarir Pol Rom…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n Itir Sios Bagha Osirizim
\mt2 O
\mt1 Rom
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Pol kamagh…®n ifonge, a mang…®va Rom…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir Krais…®n adarazir ganasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an ak…®nafarir kam osiri. A ghaze, a dughiar otevim…®n me ko ikegh, g…®n mang…® kantri Spen…®n Akar Aghuim akunam. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n, Pol bar deraghv…®ra bigha Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim…®n gun me m…®g…®a, egha Iesus…®n g…®n zuir gumazamizibar ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n gun me m…®gei.
\ip Pol faragha Rom…®n itir Krais…®n adarazi m…®g…®a ghaze, a zurara God ko m…®g…®ava, men akurvaghasa God…®n azangs…®si. Egha g…®n an ak…®nafarir kam…®n akar m…®ngarim abigha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n tuavimra e God…®n damazim…®n gumazamizir aghuibar otivigham.‚Äù (1:17) Pol kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazamiziba bar, me Judan adarasi o Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, me bar arazir kurabagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God men apangkuvigh ua me iniam. Gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais Iesus…®n itiba, God uam me inight…®, me God…®n namakabar otogh Krais Iesus…®n aveghbuabar ikiam.
\ip Kamagh…®n amiz…® God ua gumazitam o amizitam inight…®, a ik…®r…®m…®rim igiam ikiam. Ez…® God a ko itima, God…®n Duam a giz…®fa. Kamagh…®n, ovevem ko arazir kuram ua a d…®kab…®n…®va a gativaghamin gavgaviba puvat…®. Sapta 5, 6, 7, ko 8, Pol God…®n Arazibar m…®ngarim m…®g…®ava, God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim m…®gei. Pol ghaze, God…®n Duam, gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itibar aven ikia, egha men ik…®r…®m…®ribar aven ingari.
\ip Sapta 9, 10 ko 11, Pol uan os…®mt…®zir ekiar mam…®n gun m…®gei. Pol uab…® Judabar gumazir mam. Kar gumazamizir God fom…®ra ua baghav…®ra m…®seveziba. Ez…® Judan av…®rir ekiam, me ak…®rim ragha Iesus gasara. Ez…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir av…®riba, me Iesus…®n suren gumazamizibar otifi. Ez…® Judaba puvat…®. Ez…® Pol kamagh…®n m…®gei, arazir kurar kam, kar me uari men os…®mt…®zim. Me bizir ekiar God me bagh damuasa ifongezir kam me deragha a g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Ez…® Pol…®n n…®ghn…®zim, g…®n Judan gumazamizitaba uaghan Iesus…®n adarazir aven izam.
\ip Ez…® Pol…®n ak…®nafarim…®n akar abuananaba, sapta 12, 13, 14, 15, ko 16, Pol Krais…®n adarazi g…®n mangamin arazibav gei. A igharaz darazigh ifongezir arazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribagh ami. Egha a uaghan God…®n ingangarim damuamin arazim m…®g…®ava, gavman…®n apengan ikiamin arazim m…®g…®ava, igharaz darazir akurvaghamin arazim m…®gei.
\c 1
\ms1 E n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim // Krais…®n ikia tuavir kam…®n, // e God…®n damazim…®n dera
\mr (Sapta 1--4)
\s1 Pol uan aposel…®n ingangarim…®n gun m…®gei
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Aposel 9:15; 13:2; 22:21; 1 Korin 1:1; Galesia 1:15\x*K…® Pol, k…® ia bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. K…® Krais Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazir mam. Krais Iesus nan diagha ghaze, n…® God…®n aposel…®n otogham. Egha a na m…®sevegha Akar Aghuim akunamin ingangarim na gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Aposel 26:6; Rom 3:21; 16:25-26; Galesia 3:8; Taitus 1:2\x*Faraghav…®ra God akam ak…®ra ghaze, akar aghuir kam otogham. Egha akar kam inigha, an akam inigha izir gumazibav keme. Ez…® me akar kam osiriz…® a God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n iti.
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Matyu 22:42; Luk 1:32; Jon 1:14; Aposel 2:30; Rom 9:5; Galesia 4:4; 2 Timoti 2:8\x*Akar aghuir kam a God…®n Otarim…®n gun m…®gei. Otarir kam, a gumazamizibar m…®n otogha, kamagh…®n a Atrivim Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n iti.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Aposel 13:33; Hibru 9:14\x*Egha God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n tuavim…®n, God a gamiz…® a ua d…®kavigha kamagh…®n en aka, a gavgavim itir God…®n Otarim: A Krais Iesus, en Ekiam.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Aposel 26:16-18; Rom 12:3; 15:18; 1 Korin 15:10; Galesia 2:7-9; Efesus 3:8\x*God kamagh…®n ifonge, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir maba, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ik…®va an akam…®n g…®n mangam. Kamagh…®n God, Krais Iesus…®n ingangarim…®n tuavimra, a en apangkufi. Egha God, Krais bagha, aposel…®n ingangarim damuasa e at…®.
\v 6 Ez…® ia uaghan, Krais Iesus ian diagha ghaze, ia nan adarasi, ez…® ia an g…®n zui. Egha ia Iesus…®n aven itir marasi.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt D…®boboniba 6:25-26; 1 Korin 1:2-3; 2 Korin 1:1; Galesia 1:3; Efesus 1:2; 1 Tesalonika 4:7\x*God ia gifongegha ian diagha ghaze, ia nan adarasi, egh na baghv…®ra ik…®. Ez…® k…® ak…®nafarir kam ia Rom…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir gumazamiziba bagha an osiri.
\p Egha k…® ghaze, en Afeziam God ko en Ekiam Krais Iesus, aning ian apangkuvigh…®va navir am…®rizim ia dan…®ngam.
\s1 Pol Rom…®n nguibar ekiam…®n mangasa bar ifonge
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Filipai 1:3; Kolosi 1:3-4; 1 Tesalonika 1:2; 1:8\x*K…® faragh kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa. Nguazir kam…®n nguibaba bar dar itir gumazamiziba, me ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n eghaghanim barasi. Ez…® Krais Iesus na gamima, k…® bar mogh…®ra ia bagha God m…®nabi.
\v 9-10 \x - \xo 1:9-10 \xt Aposel 19:21; Rom 15:23; 15:32; 2 Korin 1:23; Efesus 1:16; Filipai 1:8; 1 Tesalonika 2:5; 2:10; 3:10; 2 Timoti 1:3; Jems 4:15\x*K…® bar God bagha pamten ingara, egha uan gavgavim sara ingari, egha an Otarim…®n Akar Aghuim akuri. God nan gara na g…®fo, k…® ia g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti. K…® God ko m…®g…®a zurara kamagh…®n an azai, a ifuegh…®va, a uab…® na bagh tuavitam at…®ght…®, k…® ia bagh iz…®va ian ganam.
\p 
\v 11 K…® kamaghsua, k…® ia damut…®, God…®n Duam amir ingangarir aghuiba, ian ikiam, eght…® ian duaba gavgavigham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ian ganasa bar ifonge.
\v 12 Nan n…®ghn…®zim kamak…®n, e uarira uarir akurvagham. Ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan akurvaght…®, nan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ian akurvagham.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Jon 15:15-16; Aposel 19:21; Rom 15:23; 16:7; Filipai 4:17\x*Nan adarasi, ia kamagh…®n fogh, k…® dughiar av…®ribar iz…® ian ganasava amima, bizir av…®riba otiva nan tuavim ap…®rima, kamagh…®n k…® izir puvat…®. K…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar tong…®n ingariz…®, men av…®riba navibagh ira. Kamagh…®ra, k…® ian tong…®n ingart…®, ian gumazamizir av…®riba navibagh iragham.
\v 14 God Grighba ko gumazamizir Grigh…®n aven itir puvat…®zibar akurvaghasa ingangarim na gan…®ngi. Fofozir gumazamiziba ko, fofoziba puvat…®zir gumazamiziba me uakan. Kamagh…®n, k…® gumazamiziba me ikarvaghamin os…®mt…®zim ater…®va, ingangarir kam damuam.
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia Rom…®n itir gumazamiziba, k…® Akar Aghuim uaghan ia m…®k…®nasa, nan navim d…®kafi.
\s1 God…®n gavgavim, an an Akar Aghuim…®n aven iti
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Onger Akaba 119:46; Mak 8:38; Aposel 3:26; 13:46; 1 Korin 1:18-24; 2 Timoti 1:8\x*K…® fo, God…®n gavgavim an Akar Aghuim…®n aven iti. Gavgavir kam gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir an itiba bar men akurvagham. A faragh Judabar akurvagh, egh uaghan Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar akurvagham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Akar Aghuim akunasa aghums…®zir puvat…®.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Habakuk 2:4; Jon 3:36; Rom 3:21-22; Galesia 3:11; Hibru 10:38\x*Akar Aghuir kam, an arazir aghuir God amizir kam…®n e d…®pon suam, e an damazim…®n dera. Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n tuavimra e an damazim…®n gumazamizir aghuibar otogham. Mati akam God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n iti, ‚ÄúGumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itiba, God me m…®k…®m suam, me nan damazim…®n dera, eght…® gumazamizir kaba zurara deraghv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\s1 Gumazamiziba bar ak…®rim God gasara
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Aposel 17:30; Efesus 5:6; Kolosi 3:6; 2 Tesalonika 2:12\x*E fo, God uan Nguibam…®n ikia uan an…®ngagharim azenimra aneka. A gumazamizir ak…®rim a gasaragha arazir kurabagh amiba, ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam. Men arazir kurar kam guiz…®n akam ab…®ri.
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Jon 1:9; Aposel 14:15-17; 17:24-28\x*God gumazamizir kaba uab…® derav…®ra men akaz…®, me an arazir av…®ribagh fo. Me guizbang…®ra fo, egha me ak…®rim God gasara, kamagh…®n amiz…®, God ivezir kuram me gan…®di.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Jop 12:7-9; Onger Akaba 19:1; Aposel 14:17; 17:27; Hibru 11:3\x*God nguazim…®n biziba bar dar ingarizir dughiam…®n ikegha, iza dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazamiziba bar a ingarizir bizibar gani. Tuavir kam…®n, gumazamiziba God…®n arazir mogomer maba derav…®ra dagh fogham. Egha me an arazir aghuibar m…®ngarim ko an gavgavir bar ekiar zurara itim g…®fos. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazitam o amizitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogh suam, ‚ÄúK…® God g…®fozir puvat…®, egha k…® os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®.‚Äù Ti puvat…®gham!
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Jeremaia 2:5; Efesus 4:17-18\x*Me God g…®fogha kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, ‚ÄúA guizbang…®ra God.‚Äù Egha an ziam fan aghua. Egha a m…®nabir pu. Puvat…®. Men n…®ghn…®ziba onganiz…® mogh…®n itima, me fofozir aghuiba puvat…®z…®, m…®tatem men n…®ghn…®ziba avaragha dagh iz…®fa.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Jeremaia 10:14; 1 Korin 1:20\x*Me ghaze, me fofozir aghuim iti. Me guizbang…®ra puvat…®gha, ongani.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt God…®n Araziba 4:16-18; Onger Akaba 106:20; Jeremaia 2:11; Esekiel 8:10; Aposel 17:29\x*Me God…®n zurara itim ak…®rim a gasara, egha an ziam fer pu. Puvat…®. Me aremeghamin gumazamizibar m…®n gara, marvir guaba ko, kuaraziba ko, as…®ziba ko, kuruziba ko, ipebar marvir guabar ingara, egha da isa dar ziaba fe.
\s1 Gumazamiziba arazir kurar igharagha garir av…®ribagh ami
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Aposel 7:42; 14:16; 1 Korin 6:18; Efesus 4:18; 1 Tesalonika 4:4\x*Gumazamiziba God ak…®rim a gasara, ez…® bizir kam bang…®n a me ataghiz…®ma men naviba ifongezir arazir kuraba me d…®kavima, me arazir bar kurar aghums…®ziba itibar uari gami.
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Aisaia 44:20; Jeremaia 13:25; 16:19; Amos 2:4; Rom 9:5; 1 Tesalonika 1:9; 1 Jon 5:20\x*Kamagh…®n amir gumazamiziba, me God…®n guiz…®n akam…®n g…®n mangan f…®r…®n, akar ifavarim…®n anet…®. Me biziba bar adar ingarizir God…®n kamnang…®n ziam fan aghuagha, uam ak…®rim ragha a gasara. Egha a ingarizir bizibar ziaba fava da bagha ingari. God a biziba bar dar m…®ngarim, kamagh…®n e zurazurara an ziam f…® mamagh…®ra ikiam! Guizbang…®ra!
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt Ofa Gami 18:22-23; Efesus 5:12\x*Me God ak…®rim a gasara, kamagh…®n God ak…®rim ragha me gasaragha me ataghiz…®, me uan aghums…®zim itir arazir kurabagh ami. Ez…® men amuiba poroghamibar arazir aghuim ategha arazir kuraba amizir igharaziba ko uari gami.
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Ofa Gami 18:22; 20:13; 1 Korin 6:9\x*Kamagh…®ra, gumaziba poroghamibar arazir aghuim ategha naviba me d…®kava mati avim men isima, me arazir kuraba gumazir igharaziba ko uari gami. Gumaziba aghums…®zir araziba uarira uari gami, egh bizir kam…®n me uarira uan arazir kurabar ivezir kuram iniam.
\p 
\v 28 Me God…®n guiz…®n fofozim suiragh a g…®n…®ghn…®ghan aghua, kamagh…®n God me ataghiz…®, me uan n…®ghn…®zir kurar m…®z…®r…®zibar g…®n ghua arazir bar kurar e damuan koghamibagh amua, n…®ghn…®ziba bar ikufi.
\v 29 Me arazir kurar av…®rir kabagh ami: men araziba bar ikuvigha, munav…®n bizim bagha navim d…®kafi, egha uarir apanim gamigha, bizir av…®riba itir gumazamiziba bagha navim ikufi, egha gumazamizibav sozima da ariaghiri, egha biziba bagha uarir atara uari ab…®si, egha gumazamizibagh ifari. Egha gumazamiziba paza me damuasa n…®ghn…®si, egha g…®rak…®rang…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kurabar gumazamizibagh ami.
\v 30 Egha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ifavarir gumazamizir igharazibar ziabagh as…®ghas…®zibagh ami. Egha God…®n apanim gamua, egha tiraghtirazir arazim gamua, egha uan navir averiabar aven ghaze erara e bar dera, egha me uari uan ziaba fe. Egha me uari arazir kurar igiar mabagh ami da otifi. Egha me uan afeziaba ko amebabar akaba batosi.
\v 31 Me n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®. Egha me uari uan akar d…®k…®r…®zibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Egha me igharaz darazir akurvaghan aghuagha, men apangkuvir puvat…®.
\v 32 \x - \xo 1:32 \xt Onger Akaba 50:18; Hosea 7:3; Rom 2:2; 6:21\x*Me fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n itir Akar Gavgavim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamizir kamagh…®n amiba, me ivezir kuram inigh ar…®m…®ghiregham.‚Äù Gumazamizir kaba God…®n Akar Gavgavim g…®fogha, me a batogha arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami. Egha uaghan me arazir kurar kabarama amir pu. Puvat…®. Me arazir kurar kabagh amir gumazamizir igharazibar ziaba fe.
\c 2
\s1 God gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®zir arazim, a guizbang…®ra ghua bar dera
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Matyu 7:1; Luk 6:37; Jon 8:7-9; Rom 1:20\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia akaba igharaz darazi gasir gumazamiziba, k…® vaghvagh kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa, n…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…® suam, k…® uab…® os…®mt…®ziba nan puvat…®. Ia orakigh, n…® akam igharazitav gasi, egha n…® uab…® arazir me amiba n…® uaghan dagh ami, kar n…® akam uaghan uab…® gasi.
\v 2 E fo, God, gumazamizir arazir kurar kabagh amiba, men araziba tuis…®gha ivezir kuram me gan…®di, arazir God amir kam a bar guizbang…®ra ghua bar dera.
\v 3 Ia arazir kabagh amir gumazamiziba akam me gasa, egha ia uari arazir kaba uaghan me ko dagh ami. N…® ghaze, God ti akam n…® gasan kogham? Bar puvat…®!
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Aisaia 30:18; Rom 3:25; Efesus 1:7; 2:9; 2 Pita 3:9; 3:15\x*Manmagh…®n amiz…® God arazir aghuibar n…® gamua, egha dughiar ruarim…®n n…® m…®zua ikia, n…®n arazir kuram bagha ivezir kuram zuam…®ra n…® gan…®ngizir puvat…®. God…®n arazir aghuarir kam, n…® ti an garima a ti pura bizim? N…® uan navim giraghasa God ifuegha arazir aghuim…®n n…® gami. N…® foz, o?
\p 
\v 5 N…® uan navim…®n suiragha gavgavigha uan navim g…®ghasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Egha arazir kam…®n n…® uab…® ivezir bar ekiar kuram uab…® gar…®si.
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Onger Akaba 62:12; Aghuzir Akaba 24:12; Matyu 16:27; Jon 5:29; 1 Korin 3:8; 2 Korin 5:10; Akar Mogomem 22:12\x*God gumazamiziba amizir araziba bagh ivezim vaghvagh me dan…®ngam.
\v 7 Gumazamizir maba arazir aghuiba bagha gavgavigha dar g…®n ghua, God ko dabirabir aghuim, ko ziar ekiam, ko ik…®r…®m…®rir ikuvighan koghamim, da iniasa tuavim buri. God ik…®r…®m…®rir zurazurara itim gumazamizir kabar an…®ngam.
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Rom 1:18; 2 Tesalonika 1:8\x*Ez…® gumazamizir maba uarira uari g…®n…®ghn…®gha, guiz…®n akam ak…®rim ragh a gasaragha arazir kurabar g…®n zui. Eght…® God uan an…®ngagharim is…® gumazamizir kabagh ingegh…®va ivezir bar kuram me dan…®ngam.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Amos 3:2; Luk 12:47-48; Rom 1:16; 1 Pita 4:17\x*Os…®mt…®zir ekiam ko m…®zazir kuram gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amiba batogham. Judaba faraght…®ma Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba g…®n.
\v 10 Eght…® God dabirabir aghuim ko ziar ekiam ko navir am…®rizim is…® gumazamizir arazir aghuibagh amibar an…®ngam. Judaba faraght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba g…®n.
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt God…®n Araziba 10:17; 2 Eghaghaniba 19:7; Jop 34:19; Aposel 10:34; Galesia 2:6; Efesus 6:9; Kolosi 3:25; 1 Pita 1:17\x*God ik…®zitam uab…®n toroghan kogh, egh bar derav…®ra gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®gham.
\p 
\v 12 Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, Moses Osirizir Araziba men puvat…®. Egha arazir kuram gamigha, Moses Osirizir Arazibar saghon ikia me ovenge. Ez…® Judaba Moses Osirizir Araziba ikia dagh fo. Egha arazir kuram gamiz…®, God men gara Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven itir akam…®n g…®n ghua men araziba tuis…®si.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Matyu 7:21; Jems 1:22-25; 1 Jon 3:7\x*E fo, gumazitam o amizitam Moses Osirizir Araziba pura da baragha, God…®n damazim…®n derazir pu. Puvat…®. Gumazamizir Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n zuibara, God me m…®g…®a ghaze, me an damazim…®n dera.
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Aposel 10:35\x*Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, me Moses Osirizir Araziba puvat…®. Egha men marazi uan n…®ghn…®zimra arazir aghuibar g…®n zui, ez…® arazir kaba Moses Osirizir Araziba m…®rara zui. Me Moses Osirizir Araziba puvat…®, egha dar aven itir arazir aghuibar g…®n zui. Arazir kam kamagh…®n en aka, arazir aghuiba men n…®ghn…®zim…®n iti me fo, me manmagh…®n damuam.
