\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Jenesis 17:5; Aisaia 48:13; 1 Korin 1:28; Efesus 2:1; 2:5; 1 Pita 2:10\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® n…® damight…® n…® kantrin av…®ribar afeziam…®n otogham.‚Äù Akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam, God uab…® a gamiz…® an an damazim…®n gavgafi. God…®n kamra, Abraham n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. Egha God…®n kamra, a gumazamizir ovengezibagh amima me ua d…®kafi, egha a pura m…®geima bizir faragha itir puvat…®ziba, da otifi.\f + \fr 4:17 \ft Grigh…®n akam, vez…®n kam deragha bigha m…®kemezir puvat…®. Marazi n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, vez…®n kam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAbraham, God…®n damazim…®n en ovavir afeziam.‚Äù\f*
