\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Rom 4:25; 5:8-10\x*E uarira uarir akurvaghan iburazir dughiam…®n, Krais e gumazamizir kuraba bagha areme. An ovevem, God inabazir dughiam…®n oto.
\v 7 Guizbang…®ra, gumazir aghuim…®n akurvaghs…® aremeghamin bizim bar oseme. Ez…® ti dughiar vabara, tarazi ti, gumazir aghuitam bagh aremegham.
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Jon 3:16; 15:13; 1 Pita 3:18; 1 Jon 3:16; 4:10\x*Ez…® e arazir kurabagh amuav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, Krais en akurvaghasa areme. Arazir kam…®n, God bar e gifongezir arazim en aka.
