\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt Jenesis 2:17; 3:6; 3:19; Rom 6:23; 1 Korin 15:21\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir vam…®ra arazir kuram gami, ez…® tuavir kam…®n arazir kuraba nguazir kam…®n oto. Ez…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba arazir kurabagh amima, ovevem oto. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar arazir kurabagh amima, ovevem bar me bato.
\v 13 \x - \xo 5:13 \xt Rom 4:15; 1 Jon 3:4\x*E fo, fom…®ra Moses Osirizir Arazibar t…®ghar otivamin dughiam, dughiar kam…®n arazir kuraba nguazir kam…®n iti. Ez…® Moses Osirizir Araziba itir puvat…®z…®, God gumazamizibar arazir kurar kaba medir puvat…®.
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt 1 Korin 15:21-22; 15:45\x*Ez…® Adam…®n dughiam…®n ikegha ghua Moses…®n dughiam…®n, ovevem gumazamiziba gativagha me avara. Gumazir maba Adam…®n m…®n arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®, men arazir kuraba ighara. Ez…® ovevem uaghan me avara. Ez…® Adam mati Gumazir Izamim…®n nedazim.
