\v 15 Ez…® God…®n apangkuvir a pura an…®ngizim, an Adam amizir arazir kuram…®n m…®n amir puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, gumazir vam…®ra Adam arazir kuram gamiz…®, tuavir kam…®n gumazamizir av…®riba ariaghire. Ez…® gumazir vam…®ra Krais Iesus an apangkuvim…®n, God e gamiz…®, e an damazim…®n dera. Ez…® God…®n apangkuvim…®n gavgavim bar ovevem…®n gavgavim gafira. Bizir kam, a gumazamizir av…®riba pura me gan…®ngiz…®, a me giz…®fa!
\v 16 Egha uaghan God puram e gan…®ngizir bizim ko, gumazir vam…®ran arazir kuram…®n otozir bizim, aning uaghara zuir puvat…®. Aning arazir vam…®ra e gamir pu. Bar puvat…®. Gumazir kam arazir kurar vam…®ra gamiz…®, God gumazamiziba me tuis…®gha ghaze, ia bar ikuvigham. Egha God puram e gan…®ngizir bizim kamak…®n, gumazamiziba arazir kurar av…®ribagh amima, God men apangkuva gari, mati me arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®.
\v 17 Guizbang…®ra, gumazir vam…®ra God…®n akam batoke, ez…® an arazir kuram…®n ovevem gumazamiziba bar me gatifa. Ez…® God uan apangkuvim gumazamiziba avaraz…® a me giz…®fa, ez…® a ghaze, ia nan damazim…®n dera. Kar a pura an…®ngizir bizim. Egh gumazir vam…®ra Krais Iesus…®n ingangarim…®n, tina God pura an…®dir bizim iniva, a Krais ko ik…®va bizibagh ativagh dar ganam. Egh me kamagh ik…®va me bizibagh ativaghamin gavgavim, ovevem…®n gavgavim gafiragham.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 5:18 \xt 1 Korin 15:22\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e derav…®ra akar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gham. Gumazir mam arazir kurar vam…®ram amiz…®, God ghaze, gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra bar ikufi. Kamagh…®ra, Gumazir Igharazir Vam…®ra arazir aghuir God…®n damazim…®n derazim gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…® God gumazamiziba bar men gari, me mati arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®. Egh God zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim me dan…®ngam.
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Aisaia 53:11\x*Gumazir vam…®ra God…®n akam baraghizir puvat…®, ez…® an arazir kam gumazamizir av…®ribagh amiz…®, me arazir kurabagh amir gumazamizibagh ava. Kamagh…®ra Gumazir Vam…®ra God…®n akam baraghiz…®, an arazir kam gumazamizir av…®ribagh amiz…®, me God…®n damazim…®n dera.
