\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Filipai 3:10-11\x*E Krais ko puegha mati an aremez…® mogh…®n areme. Kamagh…®ra, a ua d…®kaviz…® mogh…®n e a ko puegh ua d…®kavigham.
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt Galesia 5:24; 6:14; Efesus 4:22; Kolosi 2:11; 3:5; 3:9\x*E kamagh…®n fo, en navir ghurim…®n araziba, da Krais ko ter ighuvim…®n aremegha g…®vaz…®, en inivaf…®zim…®n agoroger arazir kurabar gavgavim g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e ua arazir kuram…®n ingangarir gumazamizibar ikian kogham.
\v 7 \x - \xo 6:7 \xt 1 Pita 4:1\x*Guizbang…®ra, gumazim o amizim aremeght…®, arazir kuram…®n gavgavim uam a gativaght…®, an an apengan ikian kogham.
\v 8 E ghaze, e Krais ko aremegha, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n iti, e uaghan a ko ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuir kam…®n ikiam.
