\v 9 \x - \xo 6:9 \xt Akar Mogomem 1:18\x*E kamagh…®n fo, Krais mozim…®n ua d…®kavigha g…®fa. Egh uam aremeghan kogham. Ovevem, a m…®sueght…® a uam aremeghamim…®n gavgaviba puvat…®.
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Luk 20:38; Hibru 9:26-28; 1 Pita 3:18\x*Krais dughiar vam…®ram areme, egha ua aremeghan kogham. Egha ovever arazir kam…®n, an arazir kuram…®n gavgavim ag…®fa. Eght…® ovevem uam a gativs…® damuan kogham. A dat…®r…®gh…®n ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim…®n ikia God baghav…®ra iti.
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt Rom 6:2; 2 Korin 5:15; Galesia 2:19; 1 Pita 2:24\x*Ia uaghan n…®ghn…®zir kamra ik…®, ia uaghan Krais ko aremegha arazir kuram…®n gavgavim uam an apengan itir puvat…®. Ia Krais Iesus ko puegha God baghav…®ra ikia ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim…®n iti.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 6:12 \xt Jenesis 4:7; Onger Akaba 19:13; 119:133\x*E Ovever m…®karzim iti, ez…® ia arazir kuram ateght…®ma a ian m…®karzibagh ativan mark…®. Arazir kuram ia gekut…®ma ia m…®karzim ifongezir arazir kuram…®n g…®n mangan kogham.
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Rom 7:5; 12:1; Efesus 2:5; 5:14; Kolosi 3:5; Jems 4:1\x*Egh ia arazir kuram…®n amamangat…®ght…® a ian soroghafariba ko bizitaba ik…®rar…®ght…® ia arazir kuratam damuan mark…®. Ia mati, gumazamizir ovegha mozim…®n ikegha ua d…®kavigha angam…®ra itiba, kamagh…®n ia uari is…® God dan…®ng. Egh God…®n amamangat…®ght…® a ian m…®karzim bar a gativaght…® ia arazir aghuibar amu.
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt Rom 7:4-6; 8:2; Galesia 5:18; 1 Jon 3:6\x*Arazir kuram ua ian m…®karzibagh ativan kogham. Ia Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan itir puvat…®, ia God…®n apangkuvim…®n apengan iti.
\s1 E arazir aghuibar ingangarir gumazamiziba
\p 
\v 15 \x - \xo 6:15 \xt Rom 6:1\x*E dat…®r…®gh…®n ua Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan itir puvat…®. Egh e manmagh…®n damuam? E dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n apangkuvim…®n apengan iti, egh e arazir kurabar amuv…®ra ikiam o? Bar puvat…®!
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Matyu 6:24; Jon 8:34; 2 Pita 2:19\x*Ia ti kamagh…®n fos o? Ia uari is…®, gumazitam dan…®ng…®va, an akam…®n g…®n mang…®va, an ingangarir gumazamizibar otivigham. Kamagh…®ra, ia arazir kuram…®n ingangarir gumazamizibar ik…®t…®, a ia damight…® ia aremegham. Egh ia God…®n akam baregh…®va an g…®n mang…®va an ingangarir gumazamizibar ik…®t…®, a ia damight…®, ia an damazim…®n deragham.
\v 17 Guizbang…®ra, ia faragha arazir kuram…®n ingangarir gumazamizibar ike, ez…® God g…®n ia isa, uan akam…®n apengan ia ar…®ki. Me God…®n guiz…®n akam ian sure gamiz…®, ia a inigha guizbang…®ra an g…®n zui. Ez…® bizir kam…®n, e God m…®nabi!
\v 18 \x - \xo 6:18 \xt Jon 8:32; 1 Korin 7:22; Galesia 5:1; 1 Pita 2:16\x*Faragha arazir kuraba ia ikiaghar…®ghiz…®, God ia f…®ri. Egha ia gamiz…®, ia arazir aghuibar ingangarir gumazamizibar otifi.
\p 
\v 19 Iavzika. Ian navir ghuribar n…®ghn…®ziba otevez…®, ia foghasa k…® bizir kam akar otevir is…®n zuim…®n ia m…®gei. Bizir kam guizbang…®ra, ia faragha uan m…®karziba bar da an…®ngiz…®, da arazir kurabar ingangarir gumazamizibar otiviz…®, ia arazir m…®z…®r…®ziba ko bar ikuvizir arazibagh ami. Egh dat…®r…®gh…®n ia bar uan m…®karzibar anight…®, da arazir aghuibar ingangarir gumazamizibar otivight…®, ia God…®n m…®rara zuegh ikiam.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 6:20 \xt Jon 8:34\x*Faragha ia arazir kurabar ingangarir gumazamizibar ikia, arazir aghuim…®n gavgavim…®n apengan itir puvat…®.
\v 21 \x - \xo 6:21 \xt Rom 1:32; 7:5; 8:6; 8:13\x*Ia faragha amir arazibagh da akurvazir manabar ia gami? Arazir kaba, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n dagh n…®ghn…®gha aghums…®si. Arazir kabara gumazamizibagh amima me ariaghiri.
\v 22 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n God ia f…®riz…®, ia arazir kurabar gavgavim…®n apengan itir puvat…®gha, God…®n ingangarir gumazamizibar otifi. Ia iniamin bizir aghuimra kara, God ia damight…®, ia God…®n m…®rara zuegh ik…®, zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam.
\v 23 \x - \xo 6:23 \xt Jenesis 2:17; Rom 2:7; 5:12; 5:15; Jems 1:15; 1 Pita 1:4\x*Guizbang…®ra, arazir kuram ivezim isa uan ingangarir gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Ivezir kam an ovevemra. Ez…® God bizir aghuarir pura e gan…®ngizimra kara, zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim. Ik…®r…®m…®rir kam, e uan Ekiam Krais Iesus ko poroghava a isi.
\c 7
\s1 Dat…®r…®gh…®n e navir igiam…®n arazibar g…®n ghua ingangarim gami
\p 
\v 1 Nan adarasi, ia Moses Osirizir Arazibagh foz…® k…® ia m…®gei. Ia fo, gumazamiziba angam…®ra ikiav…®ra ikia, Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan iti. Gumazamiziba aremegha uam Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan itir puvat…®.
\v 2 \x - \xo 7:2 \xt 1 Korin 7:39\x*Amizim pam ik…®t…®, an pam angam…®ra ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®ma, Moses Osirizir Araziba uaghara aning ike. Amizim…®n pam aremeght…®, Moses Osirizir Arazir uaghara aning ikezim, uam amizim ikeghan koght…® amizim f…®righ…®r…®gham.
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Matyu 5:32\x*Gumazim angam…®ra ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, amizim gumazir igharazim ko dakuight…®, me amizir kam m…®k…®m suam, a poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gamir amizim. Amizir kam…®n pam aremeght…®, Moses Osirizir Arazim a ikeghan koght…® a f…®righ…®r…®gham. Kamagh…®n, a gumazir igharazim…®n ik…®t…®, me kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham, a poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gami. Puvat…®.
