\v 4 \x - \xo 7:4 \xt Rom 6:2; 6:11; 8:2; Galesia 2:19; 5:22; Kolosi 2:14\x*Kamagh…®ra, nan adarasi, ia Krais…®n m…®karzim ko puegha bizir kam…®n ia a ko ovegha, uam Moses Osirizir Arazim…®n apengan itir puvat…®. God kamagh…®n ifonge, e a bagh ingart…® dagher aghuiba otivam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazir God amiz…® ua mozim…®n d…®kavizim, ia an adarasi.
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt Rom 6:13; 6:21; Galesia 5:19; Jems 1:15\x*E faragha uan navir ghurim…®n arazibar g…®n zuima, Moses Osirizir Araziba agoroger kuram en m…®karzibagh an…®ngiz…®ma, e arazir kuram gami. Ez…® arazir kam…®n ovevem e bato.
\v 6 \x - \xo 7:6 \xt Rom 2:29; 6:4; 8:2; 2 Korin 3:6\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n e Krais…®n m…®n ovengegha faragha en suighizir biziba, e da ataki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Moses Osirizir Araziba uam en suirazir puvat…®z…® e f…®riagh…®re. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n en ingangarir e amiba, ua Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Dat…®r…®gh…®n, God…®n Duam e gamima e tuavir igiam…®n g…®n ghua ingangarim gami.
\s1 Arazir kuraba paza e gami
