\v 7 \x - \xo 7:7 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:17; God…®n Araziba 5:21; Aposel 20:33\x*Eght…® manmak…®n? Moses Osirizir Araziba agoroger kuram en m…®karzibar anight…®, e arazir kuram damigh, manmagh m…®k…®mam? Tarazi suam, Moses Osirizir Araziba ti ikufi. Bar puvat…®. Moses Osirizir Araziba ikian koght…®ma, k…® guiz…®n kamagh…®n azangam, arazir kuraba, da tizim? K…® dagh foghan kogham. Moses Osirizir Araziba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® munav…®n biziba bagh navim d…®kavan mark…®.‚Äù A kamagh…®n m…®kemeghan koght…®, k…® foghan kogham, biziba bagha navim d…®kavir arazim, an arazir kuram.
\v 8 \x - \xo 7:8 \xt Rom 4:15; 5:20; 1 Korin 15:56\x*Ez…® arazir kuram nan navir ghurim…®n aven ingara, egha Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven tuavim…®n apigha n…®ghn…®zir kuraba na gan…®di. Egha tuavir av…®ribar nan navim gami a d…®kavima, k…® gumazamizir igharazibar bizibar gara nan navim da bagha arai. Moses Osirizir Araziba ti puvat…®z…®ma, arazir kuram gavgaviba puvat…®ghai.
\v 9-10 \x - \xo 7:9-10 \xt Ofa Gami 18:5; Esekiel 20:11-13; 20:21; Rom 10:5; 2 Korin 3:7; Jems 1:15\x*Fom…®ra Moses Osirizir Araziba itir puvat…®z…®, k…® angam…®ra iti. Ez…® Moses Osirizir Araziba otoz…®, arazir kuraba d…®kavigha angam…®ra iti k…® fo, k…® God…®n damazim…®n areme. Moses Osirizir Arazibar ingangarimra kara, a ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim e gan…®di. K…® Moses Osirizir Arazibar tuavim…®n, ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim inizir pu. Puvat…®. Da na gamiz…®, k…® areme.
\v 11 \x - \xo 7:11 \xt Jenesis 3:13; Hibru 3:13\x*Ez…® arazir kuram nan aven ingara Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven tuavim…®n apigha na gifari. Egha Moses Osirizir Arazibar tuavm…®n na m…®soghez…®, k…® areme.
