\v 12 \x - \xo 7:12 \xt Onger Akaba 19:8; 119:138; 1 Timoti 1:8\x*E kamagh…®n fo, Moses Osirizir Araziba, da God…®n otivaghire. Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven itir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgaviba, da uaghan God…®n otivaghiregha God…®n damazim…®n derazir arazibar amuasa e m…®g…®a, egha gumazamizibar akurvasi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 7:13 \xt Rom 5:20\x*Ez…® manmak…®n? Bizir aghuir kam ti na gamiz…® k…® ovenge? Bar puvat…®. Arazir kuram uab…® na gamiz…® k…® ovenge. God kamagh…®n ifonge, arazir kuram azenim gir…®ght…®ma e bar fogh suam, arazir kuram a bar bizir kuram. Kamagh…®n amiz…® God arazir kuram…®n amamangat…®z…®, arazir kuram bizir aghuir kam…®n aven otogha na gamiz…® k…® ovenge. Kamagh…®n amiz…® Moses Osirizir Arazibar tuavim…®n, God guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n en aka, arazir kuram bar kurigha mughasi.
