\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt Onger Akaba 51:5; Jon 3:6\x*E fo, Moses Osirizir Araziba, da God…®n Nguibam…®n bizim, ez…® k…® nguazir kam…®n gumazim. Ez…® arazir kuram…®n gavgavim nan suiraz…®, k…® arazir kuram…®n ingangarir gumazim…®n oto.
\v 15 \x - \xo 7:15 \xt Galesia 5:17\x*Egha k…® amir araziba, k…® deragha dar m…®ngaribagh fozir puvat…®. Arazir k…® damuasa bar ifongeziba, k…® dagh amir puvat…®. Egha arazir k…® ifongezir puvat…®ziba, k…® zurara dagh ami.
\v 16 Arazir k…® ifongezir puvat…®ziba, k…® dar amut…® nan arazir kam kamagh…®n ian akaght…®, k…® ti kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, Are, Moses Osirizir Araziba da bar dera.
\v 17 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uab…® arazir kurar kabagh amir pu. Puvat…®. Arazir kurar nan aven itimra, dagh ami.
\v 18 \x - \xo 7:18 \xt Jenesis 6:5; 8:21\x*K…® uan navir ghurim m…®gei. K…® fo, bizir aghuitam nan aven itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® arazir aghuibar amuasa ifuegha, dar amuamin gavgaviba pu.
\v 19 Arazir aghuir k…® damuasa ifongeziba, k…® dagh amir pu. Egha arazir kurar k…® damuasa ifongezir puvat…®ziba, k…® dagh ami.
\v 20 Arazir k…® aghuaziba, k…® dagh amua, kamagh…®n fo, k…® uab…® kamagh…®n amir pu. Puvat…®. Arazir kurar nan aven itimra, dagh ami.
