\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1 \xt Rom 8:34; 8:39\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…® e Krais Iesus ko pogheziba, God dat…®r…®gh…®n uan kotiam…®n aven uam ivezir kuram e dan…®ng…®s…® m…®k…®man kogham.
\v 2 \x - \xo 8:2 \xt Jon 8:36; Rom 7:23-25; 2 Korin 3:6; Galesia 2:19\x*E fo, e bar dat…®r…®gh…®n Krais Iesus ko pueghav itiba, God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim e gan…®ga, ovevem…®n arazim ko arazir kuram…®n e f…®raghar…®ki. Eght…® arazir kaba ua e gativagh e ik…®rarighan kogham.
\v 3 \x - \xo 8:3 \xt Aposel 13:38-39; 15:10; Rom 3:20; 2 Korin 5:21; Filipai 2:7; Hibru 4:15; 7:18-19\x*En navir ghuriba, gavgaviba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Moses Osirizir Araziba, en arazir kurabar g…®n amangamin gavgaviba puvat…®. Ez…® Moses Osirizir Araziba damuan koghamin bizir kam, God uab…® a gami. God uan Otarim amadaz…®, a gumazim…®n m…®n otogha, arazir kurabagh amir gumazim…®n m…®n gari. A en arazir kuraba ag…®vasa izez…®, an ingangarim…®n tuavim…®n, God gumazamiziba itir arazir kurabar gavgavim ag…®vagha a gas…®ghas…®ki.
\v 4 \x - \xo 8:4 \xt Galesia 5:16; 5:25\x*Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n navir ghurim…®n arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®, e God…®n Duam…®n arazibar g…®n zui. God kamagh…®n ifonge, Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven itir arazir aghuiba en navibar aven deragh otogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…® God en arazir kurabar gavgavim a g…®vagha a gas…®ghas…®ki.
