\v 6 \x - \xo 8:6 \xt Rom 6:21; 8:13; Galesia 6:8\x*Eght…® gumazim o amizim navir ghurim…®n araziba baghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh…®va, an aremegham. Eght…® tina God…®n Duam baghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh…®va, a ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim ko navir am…®rizim iniam.
\v 7 \x - \xo 8:7 \xt Matyu 12:34; Jon 8:43; 12:39; 1 Korin 2:14; Jems 4:4\x*Eght…® gumazim o amizim navir ghurim…®n araziba baghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh, a God…®n aghuagh…®va an apanim…®n ikiam. A God…®n otivir Moses Osirizir Arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®gha guizbang…®ra dar g…®n mangan kogham.
