\v 10 \x - \xo 8:10 \xt Galesia 2:20; Efesus 3:17; 1 Pita 4:6\x*Ia arazir kuram gamigha, bizir kam…®n ia ariaghire. Eght…® Krais ian navir averiabar aven ik…®t…®, God ia m…®k…®m suam, ia nan damazim…®n dera, eght…® God…®n Duam ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim ia dan…®ngam.
