\v 15 \x - \xo 8:15 \xt 1 Korin 2:12; 2 Timoti 1:7; Hibru 2:15\x*\x - \xo 8:15-17 \xt Galesia 4:5-7\x*E kamagh…®n fo, Duar God ia gan…®ngizim, a ia gamiz…®, ia pura ingangarir gumazamizibar otozir puvat…®, egh ia bizibar atiati. Puvat…®. God…®n Duam ia gamiz…®, ia an boribar otifi. Egha God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n e an d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ame, En Afeziam!‚Äù\f + \fr 8:15 \ft Aram…®n akam, a Iesus…®n nguibam…®n akam, me uan afeziam d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúAba.‚Äù Egha Iesus uan Afeziam ko m…®g…®a, a kamagh…®n a d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúAba.‚Äù N…® Mak 14:36…®n gan.\f*
