\v 26 \x - \xo 8:26 \xt Sekaraia 12:10; Efesus 6:18; Jems 4:3\x*Kamagh…®ra, e gavgaviba puvat…®zir darasi, God…®n Duam en akurvasi. E fozir puvat…®, e manmagh…®n biziba bagh God ko m…®k…®mam? En m…®g…®r…®g…®aba otefe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n Duam uab…® e bagha God ko m…®g…®a, tuavara, an ararem akar e m…®k…®man asazibagh afira.
\v 27 \x - \xo 8:27 \xt Onger Akaba 7:9; 139:1; Aposel 1:24; 1 Korin 4:5; 1 Tesalonika 2:4; 1 Jon 5:14\x*Ez…® God gumazamizibar navir averiaba guizbang…®ra dar gari. A uan Duam…®n n…®ghn…®zim g…®fo. Kamagh…®n, an Duam God…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua God…®n gumazamiziba bagha a ko m…®gei.
