\v 28 \x - \xo 8:28 \xt Rom 9:11; 9:23-24; Efesus 1:11; 2 Timoti 1:9\x*E fo, God bizibagh amima da v…®rara uari inigha ingara, gumazamizir bar God gifongezibagh amima, me dera. Kar gumazamizir God ua me iniasa m…®kemegha g…®vaziba, a men dia.
\v 29 \x - \xo 8:29 \xt Jon 17:22; 2 Korin 3:18; Efesus 1:5; 1:11; Kolosi 1:18; 2 Timoti 2:19; Hibru 1:6\x*Kar, gumazamizir God fom…®ra ua me iniasa m…®geiba, a me ginaba, eght…® me uaghan an Otarim…®n m…®n ikiam. Eght…® borir av…®riba ik…®t…® Krais uab…® men avebar ekiam…®n m…®n ikiam.
\v 30 \x - \xo 8:30 \xt Rom 9:24; 1 Korin 6:11; Efesus 4:4; 1 Pita 2:9\x*Ez…® gumazamizir a fom…®ra me ginabaziba, a uaghan men dia. Egha gumazamizir kaba d…®bora ghaze, ia nan damazim…®n dera. Egha gumazamizir an damazim…®n derazir kaba, a ziar ekiam ko dabirabir aghuim me gan…®ngiz…® me a ko a isi.
\s1 Bizitam e damut…®, e God e gifongezir arazim…®n saghon ikian kogham
