\v 31 \x - \xo 8:31 \xt D…®boboniba 14:9; Onger Akaba 118:6\x*E bizir kabagh foghava, manmagh…®n m…®k…®mam? E fo, God e baghv…®ra ik…®t…®, tina e d…®kab…®ragh e gafiragham? Bar puvat…®gham.
\v 32 \x - \xo 8:32 \xt Jon 3:16\x*God uan Otarim…®n suirazir pu. Puvat…®, a bar mogh…®ra e bagha ofan m…®n anen…®ngiz…®, an areme. E fo, a uan Otarim e gan…®ngi, a uaghan bizir aghuir igharaziba bar, da pura e dan…®ngam.
\v 33 \x - \xo 8:33 \xt Aisaia 50:8\x*Eght…® tina God inabazir gumazamizibar kot…®n aven akam me gasam? Puvat…®. God uab…® gumazamizir kabav g…®a ghaze, ia nan damazim…®n dera.
\v 34 \x - \xo 8:34 \xt Onger Akaba 110:1; Aposel 7:55-56; Kolosi 3:1; Hibru 7:25; 9:24; 1 Jon 2:1\x*Tinara e m…®k…®m suam, ia uan arazir kuram…®n ivezim iniam? Puvat…®, Krais Iesus, gumazir aremezim, God a gamiz…® a ua d…®kavigha, dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n agharir guvim…®n aperaghav iti. Egha anar…®ra e bagha God ko m…®gei!
