\v 35 \x - \xo 8:35 \xt Rom 8:38-39\x*Krais bar e gifongeghav…®ra iti, kamagh…®n amiz…® tina e damut…®, e Krais e gifongezir arazim…®n saghon ikiam? Puvat…®. Os…®mt…®ziba e bativam, o dughiar kuram e bativam, o gumazamiziba arazir kurabar e damuam o, m…®tiriaba en agham o, bizir daghuamiba puvat…®gham o, bizir kuram e gas…®ghas…®gham o, me e m…®soght…® e ar…®m…®ghiram, bizir kabanang e damut…®, e ti Krais e gifongezir arazim…®n saghon ikiam, o? Bar puvat…®.
\v 36 \x - \xo 8:36 \xt Onger Akaba 44:22; 1 Korin 15:30-31; 2 Korin 4:11\x*Guizbang…®ra, God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizir kaba e batifi:
