\v 3 \x - \xo 9:3 \xt Ua Me Ini 32:32\x*K…® kamagh…®n bar ifonge, God nan anabam Israel, ua men iniam. Eght…® Krais nan n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mangan koght…®, k…® an azangs…®gh a ko m…®k…®mt…®, a uan gumazamizibar tong…®n na batueght…®, nan anabam Israel nan danganim iniam. Bizir kam men akuraz…®, kamagh…®n deraghai.
\v 4 \x - \xo 9:4 \xt Ua Me Ini 4:22; 9:4; God…®n Araziba 7:6; 14:1-2; Aposel 3:25; 13:22; Efesus 2:12; Hibru 8:8-10; 9:1\x*Me Israel…®n gumazamiziba, ez…® God me d…®bora ghaze, me an boriba. Ez…® me God…®n ziar ekiam a ko a inigha g…®fa. Ez…® God uan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim me ko a gami. Egha Moses Osirizir Araziba isa, me gan…®ngi. Egha uan ziam fer arazim men akagha, me ko akam ak…®ri.
\v 5 \x - \xo 9:5 \xt Matyu 1:1-16; Jon 1:1; Rom 1:25\x*Men ovavir faragha itiba, bar ziar ekiaba iti. Ovavir kabar iza, Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim, Krais nguazir kam…®n gumazim…®n m…®n men ik…®zim…®n aven oto. Krais a God, egha biziba bar dar dapanim…®n iti. Eght…® e zurazurara Krais…®n ziam fam!\f + \fr 9:5 \ft Gumazir maba n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, vez…®n kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir abuananam e kamagh…®n a gigh…® suam, ‚ÄúGod biziba bar dar dapanim…®n iti. Eght…® e zuraram an ziam f…® mang…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù\f*
