\v 6 \x - \xo 9:6 \xt D…®boboniba 23:19; Jon 8:39; Rom 2:28; 3:3; Galesia 6:16\x*K…® kamagh…®n m…®geir puvat…®, God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim pura ghua otozir pu. Puvat…®. E fo, gumazamizir maba Israel…®n anabam…®n aven ikia, guiz…®n Israelia puvat…®.
\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt Jenesis 21:12; Galesia 4:23; Hibru 11:18\x*Abraham…®n ovaviba, men marazi guizbang…®ra God…®n boriba puvat…®. Fom…®ra God kamagh…®n Abraham m…®keme, ‚ÄúAisakra, n…®n ovavir boriba otivam.‚Äù
