\v 13 \x - \xo 9:13 \xt God…®n Araziba 21:15; Malakai 1:2-3; Luk 14:26\x*Bizir kam, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúK…® Jekop gifuegha, Ison aghua.‚Äù
