\v 14 \x - \xo 9:14 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 19:7; Jop 8:3; 34:10; Onger Akaba 92:15\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…® e manmagh…®n m…®k…®mam? E suam, God ti arazir kuram gami? Bar puvat…®!
