\v 20 \x - \xo 9:20 \xt Aisaia 29:16; 45:9; 64:8\x*Ia gumazamizir k…®niba! Ia God…®n arazir an amizim bagh an ataran mark…®! Nguazir m…®nem kamagh…®n gumazir an ingarizim…®n m…®k…®man kogham, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha kamagh…®n nan ingari?‚Äù
