\v 27-28 \x - \xo 9:27-28 \xt Aisaia 10:22-23; Rom 11:5\x*Aisaia Israelia g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n akam akuri, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, Ekiam dughiar vam…®ra gumazamizir nguazim…®n itiba bar men araziba tuis…®gh, zuam…®ra men ivezir kuram is…® me danigh…®va bar me gas…®ghas…®gham. Fom…®ra, Israelian gumazamiziba, mati ongarim…®n itir gigim…®n m…®n bar av…®raseme, ez…® pura bizim, me mark…®. Ekiam men ikiav…®ra itir varazira, ua me inigham.‚Äù
