\v 2 \x - \xo 12:2 \xt Efesus 1:18; 4:23; 5:10; 5:17; Kolosi 1:21; 1 Pita 1:14; 1 Jon 2:15\x*Ia nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamiziba amir arazibar g…®n mangan mark…®. Ia teght…®ma God n…®ghn…®zir igiaba ia dan…®ngt…® ia arazir igiabar amuam. Kamagh…®n, ia God…®n ifongiam g…®fogham, a kamak…®n: ia arazir aghuiba, ko God bar akongezir araziba, ko arazir bar deragha arazir mabagh afiraziba, ia dagh fogham.
\s1 God ingangaribar amuasa fofoziba isa e gan…®ngi, eght…® e igharaziba bagh ingangarim derav…®ra a damuam
