\v 3 \x - \xo 12:3 \xt 1 Korin 3:10; 12:7; 12:11; Galesia 2:9; Efesus 4:7\x*God uan apangkuvim…®n g…®n ghua ingangarim damuasa bizir aghuim na gan…®ngiz…®, k…® vaghvagha kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa. Ia uari f…®va p…®n uari ar…®ghan mark…®. Ia deragh n…®ghn…®gh…®va, God ia gan…®ngizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n gan…®va, tuavir kam…®n ia uari tuis…®gh.
\v 4 \x - \xo 12:4 \xt Efesus 4:16\x*\x - \xo 12:4-5 \xt 1 Korin 12:12\x*E fo, inivaf…®zir vam…®ra itima, an aven soroghafariba ko bizir maba sara iti. Ez…® inivaf…®zir kam…®n aven itir bizir kaba, vaghvagha ingangarir igharazibagh ami.
\v 5 \x - \xo 12:5 \xt 1 Korin 12:27; Efesus 4:25\x*Kamagh…®ra, e gumazamizir av…®riba ikia, dat…®r…®gh…®n Krais ko porogha inivaf…®zir vam…®ran m…®n oto. Egha inivaf…®zir kam…®n aven itir bizir kabar m…®n, e uari inigha Krais…®n poroghav iti.
\v 6 \x - \xo 12:6 \xt 1 Korin 12:28; 13:2; 1 Pita 4:10-11\x*\x - \xo 12:6-8 \xt 1 Korin 12:4-11\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God uan apangkuvim…®n g…®n ghua ingangaribar amuasa fofoziba isa mati bizir aghuibar m…®n vaghvagha e gan…®ngi. Eght…® gumazitam o amizitam, God…®n akam inigha izir fofozim ik…®va, a uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n m…®rara derav…®ra God…®n akam…®n gun me m…®k…®mam.
\v 7 \x - \xo 12:7 \xt Aposel 13:1; Galesia 6:6; 1 Timoti 5:17\x*Eght…® gumazim o amizim igharazibar akurvaghamin fofozim ik…®va, a derav…®ra men akurvagh. Eght…® gumazim o amizim igharazibar sure damuamin fofozim ik…®va, a derav…®ra men sure damu.
\v 8 \x - \xo 12:8 \xt Aposel 15:32; 20:28; 2 Korin 9:7; 1 Pita 5:2\x*Eght…® gumazim o amizim gavgavim igharaz darazir navibar an…®ngamin fofozim ik…®va, a bar derav…®ra ingangarir kam damu. Eght…® gumazim o amizim biziba isa gumazamizibagh an…®dir fofozim ik…®va, an av…®riba me dan…®ng. Eght…® gumazim o amizim ingangarim…®n faragha zuir fofozim ik…®va, a derav…®ra an apengan itir gumazamizibar gan…®va ingangarir kam damu. Eght…® gumazim o amizim igharaz darazir apangkuvamin fofozim ik…®va, a men apangkuvs…® bar akongegh mamagh…®ra ik…®.
\s1 E navir averiabar aven guiz…®n gumazamizibagh ifongegham
