\v 9 \x - \xo 12:9 \xt Onger Akaba 34:14; Amos 5:15; 1 Timoti 1:5; 1 Pita 1:22\x*Ia ifar gumazamizibagh ifongan mark…®, ia uan navir averiabar aven guiz…®n gumazamizibagh ifongegh. Egh arazir kurabar aghuagh…®va, arazir aghuibar suiragh gavgafigh.
