\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 12:18 \xt Mak 9:50; Rom 14:19; Hibru 12:14\x*Ia uari navir am…®rizim ik…®va gumazamizir igharaziba ko navir vam…®ra ik…®s…® pamtem ingar.
\v 19 \x - \xo 12:19 \xt God…®n Araziba 32:35; Aghuzir Akaba 24:29; Matyu 5:39; Rom 12:17; 13:4; Hibru 10:30\x*Nan namakar aghuiba, me arazir kuram ia damight…®, ia men arazir kuram ikarvaghan mark…®. Ia teght…®, God uab…® uan an…®ngagharim…®n tuavim…®n me ikarvagham. Ia fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven en Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúArazir kuraba ikarvaghamin ingangarim, kar nan bizim. K…® uab…® men arazir kuraba ikarvagh egh ivezir kuraba me dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\v 20 \x - \xo 12:20 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:4-5; Aghuzir Akaba 25:21-22; Matyu 5:44\x*N…® God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n damu, ‚ÄúN…®n apanim, m…®tiriam an agh…®t…®, n…® daghem a dan…®ng. Egh kuarim an p…®rt…®, n…® d…®patam a dan…®ng. N…®n arazir aghuir kam…®n a damight…®, a uan arazir kuram g…®n…®ghn…®gh bar aghums…®gham.‚Äù
