\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 8:15; Daniel 2:21; Jon 19:11; Taitus 3:1; 1 Pita 2:13\x*Gumazamiziba bar gavmanbar apengan ik…®. E fo, gavman…®n tam puram otozir puvat…®. Gavman…®n ingangariba God…®n dafarimram oto. Gavman…®n aven itir gumazamizir dapaniba bar, God uab…® me ar…®ki.
\v 2 Gumazitam o amizitam gavman…®n gumazir dapanibar akam batogh…®va, kamagh…®n a God uab…® ingangarir kam damuasa m…®sevezir gumazamizibar akaba batosi. Gumazamizir kamagh…®n amiba, me uari uan arazibar ivezir kuraba iniam.
\v 3 \x - \xo 13:3 \xt 1 Pita 2:13-14; 3:13\x*Gavmanba gumazamizir arazir aghuibagh amiba atiatim me dan…®ngasa itir puvat…®. Gavmanba gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amiba atiatim me dan…®ngasa iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® gavman…®n atiatingan koghs…®, n…® arazir aghuibar amut…®, me n…®n ziam fam.
\v 4 \x - \xo 13:4 \xt Rom 12:19; 1 Tesalonika 4:6\x*E fo, gavman a mati God…®n ingangarir gumazim, egha arazir aghuibar ian akurvaghasa ingari. Ia arazir kuram damigh gavman…®n atiating. Ia fo, gumazamizibagh as…®gh…®s…®ghamin ingangarim ko gavgavim, gavman…®n dafarim…®n iti, a puram aning…®n suirazir puvat…®. A God…®n ingangarir gumazim, ia te arazir kuram damight…®, a ian arazir kuram…®n ivezim ia dan…®ngam.
