\v 10 \x - \xo 13:10 \xt Matyu 22:40; Rom 13:8; 1 Korin 13:4-7\x*N…® gumazamizir igharazim gifongegh, arazir kuratam…®n a damighan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazim igharaz darazigh ifongegh…®va, a Moses Osirizir Araziba guiz…®n dar g…®n zui.
