\v 18 \x - \xo 16:18 \xt Filipai 3:19; Kolosi 2:4; 1 Timoti 6:5; Taitus 1:10; 2 Pita 2:3\x*Me en Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n ingangarim gamir pu. Puvat…®. Me uan inivaf…®zim ifongezir arazibar g…®n zui. Me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuiba ko m…®g…®r…®g…®ar navibagh inivibagh amuava, gumazamizir arazir kurabagh ifozir puvat…®ziba me gifara, men n…®ghn…®zibagh amima, me okam n…®ghn…®si.
\v 19 \x - \xo 16:19 \xt Matyu 10:16; Rom 1:8; 1 Korin 14:20\x*Gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n oraki, ia Akar Aghuim inigha derav…®ra an g…®n zui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ia bagha bar akonge. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, ia arazir aghuiba bar adagh fogh, egh arazir kurabar amuamin fofoziba puvat…®gham.
\v 20 \x - \xo 16:20 \xt Jenesis 3:15; Rom 15:33; 1 Korin 16:23; 1 Tesalonika 5:28; Akar Mogomem 22:21\x*Dughiar bar otevim…®n, God…®n navir am…®rizim ko dabirabir aghuarim an…®dim, a Satan…®n gavgavim gas…®ghas…®gh…®va ian amamangat…®ght…®, ia Satan d…®karaght…®ma, a ian dagaribar apengan ikiam. En Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n apangkuvim ia ko ik…®.
\s1 Gumazir maba uan akaba isa Rom…®n itir gumazamiziba bagha da amadi
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 16:21 \xt Aposel 16:1; 19:22; 20:4\x*Timoti, na ko ingarir gumazim, a uan akam isa ia bagha anemaga ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. Ez…® Lusius ko, Jason ko, Sosipater, me na ko e ik…®zir vam…®ra, me uaghan ia bagha akam amadi.
\p 
\v 22 K…® Tertius, k…® uaghan uan akam isa ia bagha Ekiam…®n ziam…®n anemadi. K…® Pol…®n akaba inigha ia bagha ak…®nafarir kam…®n da osiri.
\v 23-24 \x - \xo 16:23-24 \xt Aposel 19:29; 1 Korin 1:14; 2 Timoti 4:20\x*Ez…® Gaius uan akam isa, ia bagha anemaga ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. K…® Pol k…® Gaius…®n d…®penim…®n aven itima, a bar deragha na gami. Ez…® Sios…®n mam uaghan Gaius…®n d…®penim…®n aven uari akufi. Ez…® Erastus nguibar kam…®n Gavman…®n dag…®abar garir gumazim, ko en mav Kuartus, aning uan akam isa ia bagha anemadi.\f + \fr 16:23-24 \ft Fofozir gumazir maba uaghan ghaze, akar otevir mam uaghan vez…®n kam…®n iti. Akar kam kamak…®n. En Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n apangkuvim zurazurara ia ko ik…®. Guizbang…®ra.\f*
\s1 E God…®n ziam fam!
\p 
\v 25-26 \x - \xo 16:25-26 \xt Rom 1:5; Efesus 1:9; 3:5; 3:9; 3:20; Kolosi 1:26-27; 1 Tesalonika 3:13\x*E God…®n ziam fam! God gavgavir ekiam ikia, kamagh…®n a ia damut…® ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n suiragh gavgavigham! Bizir kam, k…® an akar aghuim akura, bizir kam uaghan a m…®gei. Akar Aghuir k…® akurim, a Krais Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim, a guiz…®n akar mogomem, bar fom…®ra azenir av…®ribar modogha iza, dat…®r…®gh…®n azenim gir…®. Guiz…®n akar mogomer kam, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar osiziriba, da gumazamizibagh amiz…®, me akar mogomer kam g…®fo. God…®n ovengan koghamim, Akar Gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, akar mogomer kaba azenim gir…®t…®, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba bar dagh fogh…®va, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ik…® kamagh…®n an g…®n mangam.
\v 27 \x - \xo 16:27 \xt 1 Timoti 1:17; 6:16; Jut 1:25\x*Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n ifonge, Krais Iesus e damut…®, e God…®n ziam fam. Anar…®ra a God, egha a uab…®ra fofoziba bar iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e zurara an ziam f…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Guizbang…®ra!
